defaultNuffield
default scholars is the practice of “mob-grazing”.  
defaultMob grazing is a school of 'natural farming' that seeks to mimic the movements of grazing plains animals on a farm scale. The approach is receiving attention around the world, thanks to pioneers who have put rem
defaultarkable achievements down to mob grazing, and their claims that it can be used to replenish soils exhausted by monocropping or boost the health of pastureland. The Royal Agricultural Society of England is currently organising a series of workshops on this 
defaultsubject.
